    ],
    "text": "Traffic Restrictions for the Mahinda Maha Perahera of the Ancient Thotagamuwa Ratpath Rajamaha Viharaya \u2013 Elpitiya Police Division",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
