    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      651.31,
      537.18,
      699.01
    ],
    "text": "The annual Mahinda Maha Perahera of the Ancient Thotagamuwa Ratpath Rajamaha Viharaya is scheduled to proceed along a section of the Galle\u2013Colombo Main Road from 1.00 a.m. on 12 July 2026.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      713.59,
      542.31,
      761.41
    ],
    "text": "The procession will commence from the temple at 1.00 a.m., proceed onto the Galle\u2013Colombo Main Road, travel up to the Werellana Petrol Station, and return to the temple along the same route.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      775.87,
      549.71,
      839.79
    ],
    "text": "To minimise traffic congestion during the procession, vehicular movement on the Galle\u2013Colombo Main Road between Hikkaduwa Junction and Kahawa Junction will be restricted. Motorists are advised to use the following alternative routes and the Southern Expressway where appropriate.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      854.37,
      349.66,
      869.91
    ],
